Description: Hyprscroller creates a window layout similar to PaperWM.
 Hyprscroller is a Hyprland layout plugin that creates a window layout similar to PaperWM.
 .
 The plugin is quite feature complete and supports gaps, borders, decorations,
 special workspace, full screen modes, overview, marks and installation through hyprpm.
 .
 Packaged for hyprland-unstable.
